data.description: ASSUMABLE 2.25% VA Loan. Significant SAVINGS on your payment! Option for the remaining difference of purchase price vs loan assumption price. Must have 10% down. 4 bedroom beauty offers modern comfort w/ country feel. In the living room you'll find a nook and wood-burning fireplace. The kitchen offers a large pantry, painted cabinets & ss appliances. Main Floor Primary suite w/ your own covered patio, plus clawfoot tub in the ensuite bath. 2 more beds downstairs w/ full bath. Upstairs includes bonus room w/ small kitchenette, office space, & full bath. Use it as a MIL quarters or Airbnb. New LVP floors, interior paint & modern fixtures. New patio cover & low-maint leaf-guard gutters. 2 bay shop w/ plumbing & electrical!
